        <mxCell id="txt_pack_v2" parent="1" vertex="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;strokeColor=#64748b;fillColor=#020617;fontColor=#e2e8f0;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacing=6;fontFamily=JetBrains Mono;" value="&lt;b&gt;Canonical Text Pack (v2 Current)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;First Principles:&lt;/b&gt; Control plane (CLI/setup), Data plane (CoT routing), Identity plane (per-device cert CN), Observability plane (recorder+SQLite+export), Access plane (WebTAK + package server).&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Backend Policy:&lt;/b&gt; FreeTAK is default backend (setup.sh); OpenTAK supported through backend abstraction.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Ports:&lt;/b&gt; OpenTAK CoT TCP :8088, OpenTAK CoT SSL :8089, OpenTAK Web/API :8443, package server :9000, FreeTAK CoT TCP :8087.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Runtime Components:&lt;/b&gt; opentakserver, eud_handler, cot_parser, postgres, rabbitmq, nginx.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Source-of-Truth Patch Model:&lt;/b&gt; install OpenTAK from fwromano/OpenTAKServer@heartbeat-fixes (source-level fixes). No runtime venv monkey-patching in Heartbeat.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Patched Features Reflected:&lt;/b&gt; flask-socketio exchange declaration, channel close/recovery ordering hardening, map_state includes EUD last_point, identity handling hardening.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Recorder Contract:&lt;/b&gt; OpenTAK recorder path is SSL client to 127.0.0.1:8089 using real cert/key; writes cot_records.db sessions/events; captures positions + markers + lines/polygons/circles.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Export Contract:&lt;/b&gt; exporter.py -&gt; gpkg_writer.py -&gt; data/exports/*.gpkg, modes: raw + gcm.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Package Contract:&lt;/b&gt; one generated package per physical device identity (no shared cert package).&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;FSA:&lt;/b&gt; S0 Unconfigured -&gt; S1 Configured -&gt; S2 Installed -&gt; S3 Starting -&gt; S4 Running Healthy / S5 Running Degraded -&gt; S6 Stopping -&gt; S7 Stopped; S8 Error + recovery via restart/reset.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Data Labels:&lt;/b&gt; D1 Control, D2 Package onboarding, D3 mTLS identity/auth, D4 CoT routing, D5 Web map state, D6 Recorder ingest, D7 SQLite persistence, D8 GPKG export, D9 GIS/ALIAS downstream.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Network:&lt;/b&gt; Tailscale/LAN mesh is the transport domain for devices + WebTAK reachability.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Ops Commands:&lt;/b&gt; setup, start, stop, restart/reset, status, package, serve, record status, export, update.">
          <mxGeometry x="30" y="1260" width="2340" height="260" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
